        <Text>Dear Editor,&#xD;
    I’m Li Hua, a freshman in our senior high school. Learning our English newspaper is recruiting a reporter for the upcoming sports meeting at the end of this month, I can hardly wait to apply for the post/position.&#xD;
    Not only do I have a passion for journalism, but also I have a good command of English writing. Besides, I also pay close attention to details, which will help me capture the fabulous moments in the sports events, bring particular insights into exercise, and expose moving teamwork among students. Last but not least, I’m outgoing and can communicate well with athletes and teachers.&#xD;
    I truly hope to seize the opportunity to practice my abilities. Looking forward to your positive reply eagerly.</Text>
